# Homepage Listing Card v3.0 — UI FREEZE

**STATUS: UI LOCK | FROZEN | SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH**

The Homepage Listing Card is frozen. Every standard homepage listing uses this component.

## Frozen (0px tolerance)

- Card: **160×260px**, radius **16px**, border **1px #E8E8E8**, shadow **0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.04)**
- Image: **160×160px**, `object-fit: cover`, radius **16px 16px 0 0**, **no overlays**
- Favourite: **28×28px**, top/right **8px**, heart **16px**, `#374151`
- Content: **100px**, padding **12px**
- Price: **18px / 700**, lh **22px**, ROVEXO purple, single line
- Title: **16px / 600**, lh **22px**, **one line** (`nowrap` + ellipsis)
- Stats row: **20px**, star/eye **14px**, text **13px / 600**

## Allowed changes

- Broken image loading
- Click / favourite behaviour
- Rating / views calculation
- Accessibility
- Performance
- Responsive **bugs** (must not alter frozen pixels)

## Prohibited

- Redesign, refactor, resize, new badges/ribbons
- Seller, location, buyer protection, condition, meta rows
- Font/layout/spacing/icon changes
- “Optimisations” that change appearance

